Outputs:
- `POST /outputs/flashcards` — generate flashcards for a topic
- `POST /outputs/quiz` — generate a quiz for a topic
- `POST /outputs/summary` — generate a summary of a document or topic
- `POST /outputs/study-plan` — generate a study plan
