- `GET /memory/study-plans` — list all study plans

Implement JWT authentication middleware. Every protected endpoint requires a valid Bearer token. The user_id must be extracted from the token and used in all database and vector search queries to ensure data isolation.

Implement request validation using Pydantic models. Every request body must be validated before it reaches the business logic.

Implement response models. Every response must be typed and conform to a Pydantic response model.

Implement rate limiting to prevent abuse. Use a sliding window rate limiter.

Implement CORS configuration for the frontend domain.

Structure the FastAPI application using routers. Each domain (documents, outputs, memory) has its own router file.

**Expected outcome:** A fully designed and implemented FastAPI backend with all endpoints, authentication, validation, and security in place.

