Log every agent state transition. When the orchestrator moves from one agent to the next, log the current state snapshot (without sensitive data), the agent being called, and the elapsed time.

Log every LLM call: model name, input token count, output token count, latency, and completion status. This is essential for cost tracking and debugging.

Log every vector search query: query text, embedding generation time, search latency, number of results returned.

Send all logs to Azure Application Insights.

